Summary: {dr}Possible UFO picture taken over grain silo
divs: Sighting DetailsMy mother stepfather and I were up in jamesport looking at the amish shops. I had taken several pictures on my phone of buildings and landscapes and that day in particular I had taken a picture of a grain silo at 2:44 pm in the afternoon.(I think)(see uploaded picture)I never noticed this until today, but up above and on the right of the shorter silo there is an object. even zoomed in I cant tell what it is its blurry. but I can tell it look cylinder shaped and black or silver metallic. it possibly looks like it also has something sticking out of it. I thought maybe it might be small bug or dirt on the camera lends on my phone but Im not sure. I was hoping you could analyze it and tell me what it is.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Jamesport
